特伦特·雷兹诺 (Trent Reznor) 和阿提库斯·罗斯 (Atticus Ross) 的《挑战者》配乐将以黑胶唱片形式发行https://www.nme.com/news/film/trent-reznor-and-atticus-ross-challengers-score-to-be-released-on-vinyl-3791955?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=trent-reznor-和阿蒂库斯·罗斯挑战者队的分数即将在黑胶唱片上发布Sam WarnerMon, 09 Sep 2024 14:02:09 +0000 Film NewsMusic NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3791955 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/challengers-vinyl.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="挑战者乙烯基" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/challengers-vinyl.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/challengers-vinyl-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/challengers-vinyl-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/challengers-vinyl-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/challengers-vinyl-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/challengers-vinyl-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>实体版现已开放预订</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/trent-reznor-and-atticus-ross-challengers-score-to-be-released-on-vinyl-3791955">特伦特·雷兹诺 (Trent Reznor) 和阿蒂克斯·罗斯 (Atticus Ross) 的《挑战者》配乐将在黑胶唱片上</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/challengers-vinyl.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="挑战者乙烯基" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/challengers-vinyl.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/challengers-vinyl-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/challengers-vinyl-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/challengers-vinyl-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/challengers-vinyl-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/challengers-vinyl-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/trent-reznor">特伦特·雷兹诺 (Trent Reznor)</a>和阿提克斯·罗斯 (Atticus Ross) 为<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/challengers"><em>《挑战者》</em></a>制作的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/challengers-soundtrack-artist-info-tracklist-and-where-to-listen-3750665">原声带</a>即将发行黑胶唱片。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/challengers-ending-explained-what-happens-art-patrick-3752235">“挑战者”结局解释：阿特和帕特里克之间会发生什么？</a></strong></li></ul><p>这部电影讲述了一名网球教练和两名球员（由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/zendaya">赞达亚</a>、乔什·奥康纳和迈克·费斯特饰演）之间的三角恋故事，该片于今年早些时候上映，获得了好评。</p><p>卢卡·瓜达尼诺 (Luca Guadagnino) 的电影广受好评的配乐现已以黑胶唱片形式发行，粉丝们<a href="https://challengers.lnk.to/scorevinyl" target="_blank" rel="noopener">现在就可以预订</a>。</p><p>该唱片以豪华对折包装形式呈现，其中包含由阿莱西奥·博尔佐尼 (Alessio Bolzoni) 拍摄的现场照片的内部对折拼贴画。还有三张主角 Tashi、Patrick 和 Art 的玩家交易卡，以及 Phil&#39;s Tire Town 保险杠贴纸。 </p><figure id="attachment_3791968" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3791968" style="width: 1200px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3791968" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/challengers-vinyl-artwork.jpg" alt="挑战者乙烯基艺术品" width="1200" height="1500" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/challengers-vinyl-artwork.jpg 1200w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/challengers-vinyl-artwork-400x500.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/challengers-vinyl-artwork-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/challengers-vinyl-artwork-696x870.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/challengers-vinyl-artwork-1068x1335.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3791968" class="wp-caption-text"> “挑战者”黑胶唱片。图片来源：Sony Music Masterworks/Jamie Bertel</figcaption></figure><p>雷兹诺之前在谈到受科技音乐影响的配乐时解释道：“卢卡说，‘如果所有的音乐都像心跳一样推动科技音乐，让电影变得有趣怎么办？’”</p><p> “这是关于兴奋的，同时也有秩序和深思熟虑的配乐，”罗斯补充道。</p><p>该原声带此前已在流媒体平台上提供，而两位作曲家<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-trent-reznor-and-atticus-ross-boys-noize-remix-of-challengers-score-3617026">则聘请 Boys Noize 对乐谱进行了半小时的混音</a>。 </p><p><iframe title="Spotify Embed：挑战者（原始乐谱）" style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="352" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/album/2NHhf3qtcoVPDEb03G8RFv?si=5FXFN8YbTiy6mpBkq1KyZQ&#038;utm_source=oembed"></iframe></p><p>这位 DJ 被选来“解构并随后重新构想”Reznor 和 Ross 的作品，Boys Noize 解释道：“将其转变为一种流畅的体验，并通过重新设计曲目、创造新元素和改变某些元素来进一步推进它，这是一个有趣的挑战。”部分——尤其是“压缩/抑制”，最终变成了超级史诗。</p><p> “与特伦特和阿迪克斯一起工作是梦想成真；他们在整个过程中都非常出色并且乐于助人。”</p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/challengers-review-zendaya-tennis-3617067"><em>《NME》</em>对<em>《挑战者》</em>的四星评论</a>中，我们说道：“特伦特·雷兹诺 (Trent Reznor) 和阿提库斯·罗斯 (Atticus Ross) 出色的、令人心潮澎湃的合成器配乐，为已经美味的蛋糕锦上添花，瓜达尼诺 (Guadagnino) 以有趣的方式运用了这些配乐，而不仅仅是在网球领域比赛序列，但也经常在对话场景中开始，以进一步强调紧张气氛。简而言之，这就是 Guadagnino 的比赛、比赛和比赛。打的好。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/trent-reznor-and-atticus-ross-challengers-score-to-be-released-on-vinyl-3791955">特伦特·雷兹诺 (Trent Reznor) 和阿蒂克斯·罗斯 (Atticus Ross) 的《挑战者》配乐将在黑胶唱片上</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
