are-made-for-walkin-cover-at-outside-lands-3782672">在八月份的 Outside Lands Festival 上的特邀嘉宾</a>，两人表演了 Nancy Sinatra 的“These Boots Are Made For Walkin”，令人难忘。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-sabrina-carpenter-bring-out-kacey-musgraves-for-these-boots-are-made-for-walkin-cover-at-outside-lands-3782672"><em>NME</em>授予 Musgraves 的新专辑《Deeper Well》三颗星</a>，称其为一张以“好坏参半的结果”引导“新的开始”的专辑。</p><p>它继续说道：“在她的第六张专辑中，这位乡村跨界明星试图继续前进，但必须克服途中音乐和抒情方面的失误。”</p><p>这位乡村明星今年早些时候还访问了英国，<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/kacey-musgraves-live-in-london-setlist-photos-3756159">在伦敦举办了一场被<em>《NME》</em>称赞为“令人着迷的精彩演出”的演出。</a>评论补充道：“这位乡村跨界明星在首都的演出为她最近的作品注入了新的活力。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-kacey-musgraves-and-nickel-creeks-reimagined-cover-of-szas-kill-bill-3791894">观看 Kacey Musgraves 和 Nickel Creek 重新设计的 SZA 歌曲《Kill Bill》封面</a>后，首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
珍娜·奥尔特加 (Jenna Ortega) 和凯瑟琳·奥哈拉 (Catherine O'Hara) 畅谈“Beetlejuice Beetlejuice”舞蹈场景：“我们全力以赴” https://www.nme.com/news/film/jenna-ortega-and-catherine-ohara-open-up-about-beetlejuice-beetlejuice-dance-scene-we-went-for-it-3791880?utm_source= rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=jenna-ortega-and-catherine-ohara-open-up-about-beetlejuice-beetlejuice-dance-scene-we-go-it-itSam Warner Mon, 09 Sep 2024 11:05:29 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3791880 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Beetlejuice-Beetlejuice-Jenna-Ortega.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="甲壳虫汁 甲壳虫汁 珍娜·奥尔特加" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Beetlejuice-Beetlejuice-Jenna-Ortega.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Beetlejuice-Beetlejuice-Jenna-Ortega-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Beetlejuice-Beetlejuice-Jenna-Ortega-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Beetlejuice-Beetlejuice-Jenna-Ortega-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Beetlejuice-Beetlejuice-Jenna-Ortega-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Beetlejuice-Beetlejuice-Jenna-Ortega-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>奥尔特加解释了奥哈拉如何启发这一场景</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/jenna-ortega-and-catherine-ohara-open-up-about-beetlejuice-beetlejuice-dance-scene-we-went-for-it-3791880">Jenna Ortega 和 Catherine O&#39;Hara 谈论“Beetlejuice Beetlejuice”舞蹈场景的帖子：“我们全力以赴”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Beetlejuice-Beetlejuice-Jenna-Ortega.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="甲壳虫汁 甲壳虫汁 珍娜·奥尔特加" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Beetlejuice-Beetlejuice-Jenna-Ortega.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Beetlejuice-Beetlejuice-Jenna-Ortega-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Beetlejuice-Beetlejuice-Jenna-Ortega-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Beetlejuice-Beetlejuice-Jenna-Ortega-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Beetlejuice-Beetlejuice-Jenna-Ortega-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Beetlejuice-Beetlejuice-Jenna-Ortega-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/beetlejuice-beetlejuice"><em>《甲壳虫汁》</em></a>的主演<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jenna-ortega">珍娜·奥尔特加</a>和凯瑟琳·奥哈拉公开了影片中的大型舞蹈场景。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/heres-every-song-on-the-beetlejuice-beetlejuice-soundtrack-3791200">这是“Beetlejuice Beetlejuice”原声带中的每首歌</a></strong></li></ul><p>这部 1988 年电影的续集刚刚在电影院上映，片尾以阿斯特丽德和迪莉娅为主角的大型歌舞场景。</p><p>奥哈拉向<em>《NME》</em>谈及设计这一时刻时解释说，他们的动作是在编舞师的帮助下自己创造的。</p><p> “你是表演艺术方面的灵感来源，”奥尔特加谈到她的搭档时说道。 “我认为它在页面上读起来是一种适当的舞蹈，你激发了一个想法。” </p><figure id="attachment_3791914" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3791914" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3791914" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Beetlejuice-Beetlejuice.jpg" alt="甲虫汁 甲虫汁" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Beetlejuice-Beetlejuice.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Beetlejuice-Beetlejuice-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Beetlejuice-Beetlejuice-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Beetlejuice-Beetlejuice-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Beetlejuice-Beetlejuice-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Beetlejuice-Beetlejuice-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3791914" class="wp-caption-text">甲虫汁 甲虫汁。图片来源：华纳兄弟/Parisa Taghizadeh</figcaption></figure><p>奥哈拉阐述道：“我想要更多……对我来说不合逻辑……舞蹈动作在所有现代舞中毫无意义……不是所有现代舞，现代舞都很棒。”</p><p>奥特加回忆道：“我们当时就在片场外的一个帐篷里，我们当时想，‘哦，你这样做真是太有趣了。’”奥哈拉补充道，她的同伴“躺在地板上，做了一个戏剧性的姿势”，他们“全力以赴”。</p><p> <em>《甲壳虫汁》</em>讲述了迪茨家族三代人返回冬河的故事，莉迪亚（薇诺娜·瑞德饰）的女儿阿斯特丽德意外地打开了通往来世的大门。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="甲壳虫汁 甲壳虫汁 |官方预告片 2" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/As-vKW4ZboU?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>迈克尔·基顿（Michael Keaton）回归饰演参宿四，贾斯汀·塞洛克斯（Justin Theroux）、莫妮卡·贝鲁奇（Monica Bellucci）和威廉·达福（Willem Dafoe）也与奥尔特加一起加入。</p><p>在《NME》对<em>《甲壳虫汁》</em>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/beetlejuice-beetlejuice-review-jenna-ortega-tim-burton-3791317"><em>四星</em>评论</a>中，我们说这部电影是由导演蒂姆·伯顿的“邪恶想象力”组成的，并且“充满了极其荒谬的时刻”。</p><p> “这部电影有其缺陷，尤其是一些不必要的 CGI 沙虫与其他地方庸俗的实际效果相冲突，但它的乐趣从未减弱。这很愚蠢、令人眼花缭乱，而且有点恶心——这正是我们想要从<em>Beetlejuice</em>得到的东西。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/jenna-ortega-and-catherine-ohara-open-up-about-beetlejuice-beetlejuice-dance-scene-we-went-for-it-3791880">Jenna Ortega 和 Catherine O&#39;Hara 谈论“Beetlejuice Beetlejuice”舞蹈场景的帖子：“我们全力以赴”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
